Test Suites
TC-01 | Player Initialisation
4 passed
Player spawns at canvas centre
Player starts with 100 HP
Player starts with zero velocity
Player bubble radius is 52


TC-02 | Player Movement — WASD Input
5 passed
Pressing D accelerates player rightward
Pressing A accelerates player leftward
Pressing W accelerates player upward
Pressing S accelerates player downward
No keys: velocity decays toward zero (friction)


TC-03 | Player Boundary Clamping
4 passed
Player cannot move beyond left edge
Player cannot move beyond right edge
Player cannot move beyond top edge
Player cannot move beyond bottom edge
TC-04 | Speed Cap
1 passed
Velocity is capped at player.speed (3.5)


TC-05 | Health Display Values
3 passed
Health percentage is correct at full health
Health percentage rounds correctly at 50 HP
Health percentage is 0 at death


TC-06 | Passive Health Regeneration (FR-03)
4 passed
Health increases by ~0.03 per frame when below max
Health does not exceed maxHealth
Max health grows over time (capped at 200)
Max health never exceeds 200


TC-07 | Ammo Regeneration (FR-12)
4 passed
Torpedo ammo regenerates after 180 frames
Nova Burst ammo regenerates after 300 frames
Ammo does not exceed maximum (torpedo max = 12)
Regen timer increments each frame when ammo is not full


TC-08 | Collision Detection
4 passed
Circles touching exactly report collision
Distant circles do not collide
Concentric circles collide
Collision is symmetric


